headline: Analysts weigh outlook as UK economy returns to growth in November
summary: Investing.com -- The UK economy rebounded in November 2025 after a disappointing October, with GDP growing 0.3% month-on-month according to data from the Office for National Statistics. The manufacturing sector led the recovery with 2.1% growth, boosted by the resumption of operations at Jaguar Land Rover following a cyber attack.
